{"title":"linux+python+virtual environment","date":"2019-10-08T03:49:31.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Oct 8, 2019","L":"10/08/2019","MM-DD":"10-08"},"link":"undefined/Linux+python+virtual environment","comments":true,"tags":["Linux","server"],"updated":"2019-10-08T03:49:31.000Z","content":"<p>通常实验室里一个服务器是大家公用的，为了不引起包冲突，创建一个虚拟环境是很有必要的。通常实验室里一个服务器是大家公用的，为了不引起包冲突，创建一个虚拟环境是很有必要的。</p>\n<h2 id=\"method1\">Method1<a title=\"#method1\" href=\"#method1\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"步骤如下：\">步骤如下：<a title=\"#步骤如下：\" href=\"#步骤如下：\"></a></h3>\n<p>我将用conda来创建</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>检查是否安装conda以及当前conda版本</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">conda -V</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>查看当前已创建的虚拟环境有哪些</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">conda env list</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>或</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">conda info -e</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>创建一个名为 env1 且python解析器为2.7版本的虚拟环境</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">conda create -n env1 python=2.7</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>由此，虚拟环境可在Anaconda安装目录envs文件夹下找到。</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"使用\">使用<a title=\"#使用\" href=\"#使用\"></a></h3>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>使用激活</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">source activate env1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>给env1安装额外的包</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">conda install -n env1 [package]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>即可安装package到新创建的env1中。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>关闭环境</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">source deactivate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>移除虚拟环境</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>移除env1环境中的某个包</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">conda remove --name $env1 $package_name</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>移除某个虚拟环境</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">conda remove -n env1 --all</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"method2\">Method2<a title=\"#method2\" href=\"#method2\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"1-create-a-virtual-environment\">1 Create a virtual environment<a title=\"#1-create-a-virtual-environment\" href=\"#1-create-a-virtual-environment\"></a></h3>\n<p><code>python3 -m venv env_name</code></p>\n<p>or</p>\n<p><code>virtualenv env_name</code></p>\n<p>if env_name is not exist, there will be a dir  created.</p>\n<h3 id=\"2-activate-ur-virtual-environment\">2 Activate ur virtual environment<a title=\"#2-activate-ur-virtual-environment\" href=\"#2-activate-ur-virtual-environment\"></a></h3>\n<p>if Windows:</p>\n<p><code>env_name\\Scripts\\activate.bat</code></p>\n<p>if Unix or MacOS:</p>\n<p><code>source env_name/bin/activate</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"3-exit-environment\">3 exit environment<a title=\"#3-exit-environment\" href=\"#3-exit-environment\"></a></h3>\n<p><code>deactivate</code></p>\n","prev":{"title":"GPU manual for the poor","link":"undefined/GPU manual for the poor"},"next":{"title":"hexo's usage","link":"undefined/hexo usage"},"plink":"http://thswind.github.io/undefined/Linux+python+virtual environment/","toc":[{"id":"method1","title":"Method1","index":"1","children":[{"id":"步骤如下：","title":"步骤如下：","index":"1.1"},{"id":"使用","title":"使用","index":"1.2"}]},{"id":"method2","title":"Method2","index":"2","children":[{"id":"1-create-a-virtual-environment","title":"1 Create a virtual environment","index":"2.1"},{"id":"2-activate-ur-virtual-environment","title":"2 Activate ur virtual environment","index":"2.2"},{"id":"3-exit-environment","title":"3 exit environment","index":"2.3"}]}],"reading_time":"314 words in 2 min"}